hh3cVoiceEntityControl.name: hh3cVoiceEntityControl

revisions.description: The initial version of this MIB file.

hh3cVoiceEntityControl.contactinfo: Platform Team H3C Technologies Co., Ltd. Hai-Dian District Beijing P.R. China http://www.h3c.com Zip: 100085
hh3cVoiceEntityControl.description: This MIB file is to provide the definition of voice dial control configuration.

hh3cVoEntityCreateTable.name: hh3cVoEntityCreateTable
hh3cVoEntityCreateTable.description: The table contains the voice entity information that is used to create an ifIndexed row.

hh3cVoEntityIndex.name: hh3cVoEntityIndex
hh3cVoEntityIndex.description: An arbitrary index that uniquely identifies a voice entity.

hh3cVoEntityType.name: hh3cVoEntityType
hh3cVoEntityType.description: Specify the type of voice related encapsulation.

hh3cVoEntityRowStatus.name: hh3cVoEntityRowStatus
hh3cVoEntityRowStatus.description: This object is used to create, delete or modify a row in this table. The hh3cVoEntityType object should not be modified once the new row has been created.

hh3cVoEntityCommonConfigTable.name: hh3cVoEntityCommonConfigTable
hh3cVoEntityCommonConfigTable.description: This table contains the general voice entity information.

hh3cVoEntityCfgIndex.name: hh3cVoEntityCfgIndex
hh3cVoEntityCfgIndex.description: An arbitrary index that uniquely identifies a voice entity.

hh3cVoEntityCfgCodec1st.name: hh3cVoEntityCfgCodec1st
hh3cVoEntityCfgCodec1st.description: This object indicates the first desirable CODEC of speech of this dial entity.

hh3cVoEntityCfgCodec2nd.name: hh3cVoEntityCfgCodec2nd
hh3cVoEntityCfgCodec2nd.description: This object indicates the second desirable CODEC of speech of this dial entity.

hh3cVoEntityCfgCodec3rd.name: hh3cVoEntityCfgCodec3rd
hh3cVoEntityCfgCodec3rd.description: This object indicates the third desirable CODEC of speech of this dial entity.

hh3cVoEntityCfgCodec4th.name: hh3cVoEntityCfgCodec4th
hh3cVoEntityCfgCodec4th.description: This object indicates the forth desirable CODEC of speech of this dial entity.

hh3cVoEntityCfgDSCP.name: hh3cVoEntityCfgDSCP
hh3cVoEntityCfgDSCP.description: This object indicates the DSCP(Different Service Code Point) value of voice packets.

hh3cVoEntityCfgVADEnable.name: hh3cVoEntityCfgVADEnable
hh3cVoEntityCfgVADEnable.description: This object indicates whether the VAD(Voice Activity Detection) is enabled.

hh3cVoEntityCfgOutbandMode.name: hh3cVoEntityCfgOutbandMode
hh3cVoEntityCfgOutbandMode.description: This object indicates the DTMF(Dual Tone Multi-Frequency) outband type of this dial entity.

hh3cVoEntityCfgFaxLevel.name: hh3cVoEntityCfgFaxLevel
hh3cVoEntityCfgFaxLevel.description: This object indicates the fax level of this dial entity.

hh3cVoEntityCfgFaxBaudrate.name: hh3cVoEntityCfgFaxBaudrate
hh3cVoEntityCfgFaxBaudrate.description: This object indicates the fax baudrate of this dial entity.

hh3cVoEntityCfgFaxLocalTrainPara.name: hh3cVoEntityCfgFaxLocalTrainPara
hh3cVoEntityCfgFaxLocalTrainPara.description: This object indicates the fax local train threshold of this dial entity.

hh3cVoEntityCfgFaxProtocol.name: hh3cVoEntityCfgFaxProtocol
hh3cVoEntityCfgFaxProtocol.description: This object indicates the fax protocol of this dial entity.

hh3cVoEntityCfgFaxHRPackNum.name: hh3cVoEntityCfgFaxHRPackNum
hh3cVoEntityCfgFaxHRPackNum.description: This object indicates the high speed redundancy packet numbers of t38 and standard-t38.

hh3cVoEntityCfgFaxLRPackNum.name: hh3cVoEntityCfgFaxLRPackNum
hh3cVoEntityCfgFaxLRPackNum.description: This object indicates the low speed redundancy packet numbers of t38 and standard-t38.

hh3cVoEntityCfgFaxSendNSFEnable.name: hh3cVoEntityCfgFaxSendNSFEnable
hh3cVoEntityCfgFaxSendNSFEnable.description: This object indicates whether sends NSF(Non-Standard Faculty) to fax of this dial entity.

hh3cVoEntityCfgFaxTrainMode.name: hh3cVoEntityCfgFaxTrainMode
hh3cVoEntityCfgFaxTrainMode.description: This object indicates the fax train mode of this dial entity.

hh3cVoEntityCfgFaxEcm.name: hh3cVoEntityCfgFaxEcm
hh3cVoEntityCfgFaxEcm.description: This object indicates whether the ECM(Error Correct Mode) is enabled.

hh3cVoEntityCfgPriority.name: hh3cVoEntityCfgPriority
hh3cVoEntityCfgPriority.description: This object indicates the priority of this dial entity.

hh3cVoEntityCfgDescription.name: hh3cVoEntityCfgDescription
hh3cVoEntityCfgDescription.description: This object indicates the textual description of this dial entity.

hh3cVoPOTSEntityConfigTable.name: hh3cVoPOTSEntityConfigTable
hh3cVoPOTSEntityConfigTable.description: This table contains the POTS(Public Switched Telephone Network) entity information.

hh3cVoPOTSEntityConfigIndex.name: hh3cVoPOTSEntityConfigIndex
hh3cVoPOTSEntityConfigIndex.description: An arbitrary index that uniquely identifies a voice entity.

hh3cVoPOTSEntityConfigPrefix.name: hh3cVoPOTSEntityConfigPrefix
hh3cVoPOTSEntityConfigPrefix.description: This object indicates the prefix which is added to the called number.

hh3cVoPOTSEntityConfigSubLine.name: hh3cVoPOTSEntityConfigSubLine
hh3cVoPOTSEntityConfigSubLine.description: This object indicates the voice subscriber line of this dial entity.

hh3cVoPOTSEntityConfigSendNum.name: hh3cVoPOTSEntityConfigSendNum
hh3cVoPOTSEntityConfigSendNum.description: This object indicates the digit of phone number to be sent to the destination. 0..31: Number of digits (that are extracted from the end of a number) to be sent, in the range of 0 to 31. It is not greater than the total number of digits of the called number. 65534: Sends all digits of a called number. 65535: Sends a truncated called number.

hh3cVoVoIPEntityConfigTable.name: hh3cVoVoIPEntityConfigTable
hh3cVoVoIPEntityConfigTable.description: This table contains the VoIP entity information.

hh3cVoVoIPEntityCfgIndex.name: hh3cVoVoIPEntityCfgIndex
hh3cVoVoIPEntityCfgIndex.description: An arbitrary index that uniquely identifies a voice entity.

hh3cVoVoIPEntityCfgTargetType.name: hh3cVoVoIPEntityCfgTargetType
hh3cVoVoIPEntityCfgTargetType.description: This object indicates the type of the session target of this entity.

hh3cVoVoIPEntityCfgTargetAddrType.name: hh3cVoVoIPEntityCfgTargetAddrType
hh3cVoVoIPEntityCfgTargetAddrType.description: The IP address type of object hh3cVoVoIPEntityCfgTargetAddr.

hh3cVoVoIPEntityCfgTargetAddr.name: hh3cVoVoIPEntityCfgTargetAddr
hh3cVoVoIPEntityCfgTargetAddr.description: This object indicates the target IP address.

hh3cVoEntityNumberTable.name: hh3cVoEntityNumberTable
hh3cVoEntityNumberTable.description: The table contains the number management information.

hh3cVoEntityNumberEntry.name: hh3cVoEntityNumberEntry
hh3cVoEntityNumberEntry.description: The entry of hh3cVoEntityNumberTable. Hh3cVoEntityIndex is used to uniquely identify these numbers registered on the server. The same value of hh3cVoEntityIndex used in the corresponding HH3CVoEntityCommonConfigTable is used here.

hh3cVoEntityNumberAuthUser.name: hh3cVoEntityNumberAuthUser
hh3cVoEntityNumberAuthUser.description: This object indicates the username of the entity number to authorize.

hh3cVoEntityNumberPasswordType.name: hh3cVoEntityNumberPasswordType
hh3cVoEntityNumberPasswordType.description: This object indicates the password type of the entity number to authorize. The encrypting type of password: 0 : password simple, means password is clean text. 1 : password cipher, means password is encrypted text. default is 65535.

hh3cVoEntityNumberPassword.name: hh3cVoEntityNumberPassword
hh3cVoEntityNumberPassword.description: This object indicates the password of the entity number to authorize.

hh3cVoEntityNumberStatus.name: hh3cVoEntityNumberStatus
hh3cVoEntityNumberStatus.description: This object indicates the current state of the entity number.

hh3cVoEntityNumberExpires.name: hh3cVoEntityNumberExpires
hh3cVoEntityNumberExpires.description: This is the interval time for entity number updating registered message.
